{"tid":887365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【靚絕五台山】藍潔瑛半生坎坷 傳遭影壇大哥性侵","createTime":"2018-11-03T00:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T01:05:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3063bee005500fcee3cf7a8d3cb8e8d72d29e9ae","tid":887365,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T00:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181103/large/1541203647_30f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181103%2Flarge%2F1541203647_30f3.jpg&h=02a8c53b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終年55歲的藍潔瑛演出多部電視劇，早年有「靚絕五台山」封號，可惜後半生坎坷，最後落得暴斃家中下場。在周星馳經典電影《齊天大聖東遊記》（又名《大話西遊》）飾演蜘蛛精「春三十娘」，美豔形象深入人心，其後卻逐漸淡出演藝圈，屢被拍到頂著白髮遊蕩街頭，2015年她難得受訪，將原本的白髮染成黑髮，其後需靠救濟金度日，以及由朋友接濟。<br />\n4年前一度傳出已搬到深圳定居，圈內人甚難與她聯繫。她近年被拍到不少看來嚇人的照片，引來支持者不平，認為被媒體醜化，指她已很少出門，一定是怕出門就被偷拍掉入陷阱。<br />\n2013年12月，香港雜誌&quot;Next Magazine&quot;發布了一個訪問影片，內容為藍潔瑛親述自己早年遭到兩位「影壇大哥」性侵的經歷。 影片中對話人提出了兩位「影壇大哥」的名字，但此錄音被刪除掉。影片反響極大，引起不少媒體和網上討論的推測，但藍潔瑛和知情的好友依然拒絕點名。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181103/58869488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181103%2F58869488&d=uAEzzDC6Oflb2NFRLFWiNRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=afce1083\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181103%2F58869488&h=c145459b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181103/58869488</a>"},{"pid":"0d1fda697e8d88d76d8b1aec21918d755ded1e89","tid":887365,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T00:26:36.000Z","msg":"不留刀有潛規則...做藝人就要有覺悟羅 不過真系不幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d135e50b6ac824dd74b6eafd85c15cd8a8efb68","tid":887365,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d1fda697e8d88d76d8b1aec21918d755ded1e89","tid":887365,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T00:26:36.000Z","msg":"不留刀有潛規則...做藝人就要有覺悟羅 不過真系不幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T01:05:06.000Z","msg":"即係受害人被人姦完都要當冇事發生，呢d係咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}